# 完成說明 - 純邊驅動動作架構

## 變更摘要
動作執行邏輯已從「讀取節點動作」改為「讀取邊 (連結) 的動作」。

## 變更的檔案

### PathPlanningTracker.cs
- 新增 `_currentNavigationEdge` 欄位
- 新增 `CurrentNavigationEdge` 公開屬性
- [SelectNextTarget()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#1384-1729) 現在會查詢並設定當前導航邊
- 移除舊的「節點動作注入」邏輯

### MainForm.cs
- 新增 `using ArtaleAI.Core.Domain.Navigation`
- 動作讀取改為：`Tracker.CurrentNavigationEdge.ActionType`
- 將 `NavigationActionType` 轉換為 `PathActionType` 供既有邏輯使用

## Verification Results
### Static Rope Injection
- **Build Status**: Success. Fixed compilation errors regarding `PathActionType`.
- **Logic Verification**:
    - [InjectRopeNodes](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#554-642) successfully integrated.
    - Uses `Keys=["up"]` to trigger [ClimbUp](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#2118-2142) action correctly.
    - Uses `Keys=[]` (Empty) for rope exit node to default to `Idle`, allowing next waypoint to dictate movement.
- **Next Steps**: User to run the application and verify physical movement.

## 新架構運作方式

```
3. 存入 _currentNavigationEdge
4. MainForm 讀取 CurrentNavigationEdge.ActionType 執行動作
```

